<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-1939] Build fails if java.home has &lt;=2 path components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1939</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For &lt;tt&gt;JAVA_HOME=/opt/openjdk-bin-11.0.11_p9&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;SystemUtilsTest.PlainUnitTests.incorrectJdkPath()&lt;/tt&gt; throws a NPE at &lt;tt&gt;SystemUtils.toJdkHomeFromJvmExec(SystemUtils.java:91)&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Trivial fix will follow soon&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Gentoo Linux openjdk-bin-11.0.11_p9</environment>
